| ... | ... | ... | ... |

## All Open Questions

| Question | Raised In | Blocks |
|----------|-----------|--------|
| Domain data location? | Topic 1A | Architecture |
| ... | ... | ... |
```

**Idempotency:** If `chunk_summary.md` exists and is newer than all chunk summaries, skip this step.

Mark Stage 3 complete in TodoWrite before proceeding.

