**Key outcomes:**

1. [Outcome 1]
2. [Outcome 2]
3. [Outcome 3]

## Attendees

| Name         | Team   | Role in Sessions                        |
| ------------ | ------ | --------------------------------------- |
| [[Person 1]] | Team A | Led Topic 1, contributed to Topics 2-4  |
| [[Person 2]] | Team B | Key contributor on Standards discussion |

## Sessions Overview

### Day 1: [Date]

